1.查看Emacs快速指南
Emacs comes with a tutorial. It doesn’t take long to go through, and you will better understand and be more productive in Emacs afterward.
Type ‘C-h t’ (hold down Control while hitting ‘h’, then hit ‘t’).
To read the tutorial in a language other than english, use the command ‘help-with-tutorial-spec-language’ (hold down ‘Alt’ while hitting ‘x’, then type ‘help-with-tutorial-spec-language’ and ‘RET’). Currently available tutorial languages include: ‘bg’, ‘cn’, ‘cs’, ‘de’, ‘es’, ‘fr’, ‘it’, ‘ja’, ‘ko’, ‘nl’, ‘pl’, ‘ro’, ‘ru’, ‘sk’, ‘sl’, ‘sv’, ‘th’, and ‘zh’.

快速指南摘要

 光标移动：

											M-< 文件首

								                             上一行 C-p
								                                  :
								            M-b向左移一个词....     :        M-f向右移一个词....
					C-a行首                     向左移 C-b .... 目前光标位置 .... 向右移 C-f				C-e 行尾
								                                  :
								                                  :
								                             下一行 C-n
								            M-> 文件尾



 命令：
 	C-u 重复命令 ex: C-u 8 C-p .... 向上移动8行
 	C-g 取消命令 ex: C-u 8 C-g .... 后面的操作不会有 C-u的命令影响

 窗口:
 	C-x 1 .... 关闭其它窗口

 插入删除:
 	<Delback> 	....删除前一个
 	C-d       	....删除后一个
 	M-<Delback> ....移除前一个词
 	M-d			....移除后一个词
 	C-k			....移除光标至行尾
 	M-k			....移除光标至句尾
 	C-y			.... 召回移除
 	C-x u/C-_   .... 回退

 文件
 	C-x C-f		....打开/新建一个文件
 	C-x C-s		....储存文件
 	





